{"id":189364,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/少林寺悬赏五万追查网络造谣者/","date":"2011-10-17T09:30:03Z","modified":"2011-10-17T09:30:03Z","title":"少林寺悬赏五万追查网络造谣者","content":"<p>少林寺方丈释永信最近备受网络谣言的困扰，嵩山少林寺发表声明悬赏网络造谣者。 “少林寺方丈释永信包养北大女学生并育有一子”的网络传言沸沸扬扬。媒体引述少林寺方丈室相关负责人称，传言都是由拆迁矛盾引起的，“造谣者主要目的是为报复”。为击破谣言，少林寺表示，如果有人掌握有历次传闻中所指释永信方丈的任何不法、犯戒等确凿证据，可以第一时间向少林寺僧团举报。如果举报人提供的证据被有关方面查实确凿、有助于执法部门破案，少林寺都将给予5万元人民币奖励。少林寺还将邀请若干代表免费到少林寺调查、体验两天。<img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/19539aa0/mf.gif\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E5%B0%91%E6%9E%97%E5%AF%BA%E6%82%AC%E8%B5%8F%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%87%E8%BF%BD%E6%9F%A5%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E9%80%A0%E8%B0%A3%E8%80%85&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F17%2F0312220%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E5%B0%91%E6%9E%97%E5%AF%BA%E6%82%AC%E8%B5%8F%E4%BA%94%E4%B8%87%E8%BF%BD%E6%9F%A5%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E9%80%A0%E8%B0%A3%E8%80%85&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F10%2F17%2F0312220%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/115974796748/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/19539aa0/a2.htm\"><img src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/115974796748/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/19539aa0/a2.img\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Td3T7UvyenE:tc8hqe5VHt0:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=Td3T7UvyenE:tc8hqe5VHt0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" bord